GtkGraph Struct Reference

#include <gtkgraph.h>

Detailed Description

GtkGraph structure is the parent structure of a GtkGraph This is an opaque structure and its contents should not be written to directly. A GtkGraph is created with gtk_graph_new() and its components are modified using the many available API functions
